{"tid":846523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美帝巨棒] Pence to deliver major policy speech on China","createTime":"2018-10-03T13:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T14:21:22.000Z","uid":42921,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"60301468b4e6c488fedc9eddbe00c17319c4ed70","tid":846523,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"Pence to deliver major policy speech on China<br />\n<br />\nUS Vice President Mike Pence will make a major policy speech on China on Thursday, according to the think-tank where he will deliver his remarks.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;We are honoured to announce that Vice President Mike Pence will deliver a major speech on the administration's policy towards China at Hudson Institute on Thursday,&quot; Kenneth Weinstein, president and CEO of Hudson Institute, a top American think-tank said on Tuesday.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Hudson welcomes the vice president back to the Institute for this timely discussion on efforts to protect America's democracy and strengthen our national security, Weinstein said.<br />\n<br />\nPence's speech comes a week after President Donald Trump accused China of meddling in domestic politics and American elections."},{"pid":"49c52aa85f515f19ef6259e316d32cbbca58cd7b","tid":846523,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7eea40b2c3842e7078e3367defc4db20d58cbbd","tid":846523,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:14:40.000Z","msg":"無乜新聞報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s